<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>صفحة سطر ١٤٩ <span class="c2">(غير)</span> : بِالْكَسْرِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٥٠ ١٩ <span class="c2">(وفى اخْتِلَاف الحَدِيث)</span> إِلَخ. وفى الرسَالَة <span class="c2">(ص ١٤٣)</span> ١٥١ ١٢ <span class="c2">(وراجع الْأُم)</span> إِلَخ، والرسالة <span class="c2">(ص ١٤٤- ١٤٥)</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٥٥ ١٨ <span class="c2">(انْظُر)</span> إِلَخ.<span class="c5"> وَانْظُر الْكَلَام عَلَيْهِ:</span> فى معالم السّنَن <span class="c2">(ج ٣ ص ١٢- ١٨)</span> وَالْفَتْح <span class="c2">(ج ٦ ص ١٢٤- ١٢٨)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٦٢ ٢٠ <span class="c2">(وَانْظُر)</span> إِلَخ. وراجع فى مَنَاقِب الْفَخر <span class="c2">(ص ٩٤- ٩٥)</span> : الِاعْتِرَاض على أَن الْفَقِير أَشد حَالا من الْمِسْكِين وَالْجَوَاب عَنهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١٦٤ ١٥ <span class="c2">(حذف أَن.. وأغلب)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١٦٥ ١٣ <span class="c2">(والاستقراض)</span> تحذف الْهمزَة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١٦٨ ١٠ يحذف رقم <span class="c2">(٨)</span> ، وَيُوضَع بدله رقم <span class="c2">(٩)</span> الْمُتَأَخر.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١٧٥ ١٧ <span class="c2">(بعض مَا ورد فى ذَلِك)</span> . وراجع فى مَنَاقِب الْفَخر <span class="c2">(ص ١٠٧)</span> تَوْجِيه احتجاج الشَّافِعِي بِحَدِيث: <span class="c2">«أَيّمَا امْرَأَة أنكحت نَفسهَا»</span> إِلَخ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">١٧٨ ١٩ يُزَاد فى أَوله:</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span> فراجع كَلَامه <span class="c2">(ص ٣٨- ٣٩)</span> .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١٨٤ ١٩ <span class="c2">(لمعنيين)</span> .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٨٥ ٨ <span class="c2">(فأعرضوا)</span> : تحذف الْهمزَة.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١٩١ ١٦ <span class="c2">(أمرهَا)</span> .<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٢٠٦ ٧ <span class="c2">(الْقُلُوب)</span> .<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٢١٩ ٤ مَا رَوَاهُ يُونُس، ذكر فى مَنَاقِب ابْن أَبى حَاتِم <span class="c2">(ص ٩٦- ٩٧)</span> .<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٢٢٠ ١١ <span class="c2">(وتأمله)</span> . وَانْظُر مَنَاقِب الْفَخر <span class="c2">(ص ١٠٨)</span> .<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٢٢٤ ٢١ <span class="c2">(انْظُر الْأُم ج ٣)</span> .<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٢٢٨ ١٧ <span class="c2">(حَدِيث امْرَأَة)</span> .<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٢٣٦ ٩ <span class="c2">(مَوَاضِع)</span> .<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٢٣ <span class="c2">(رَاجع)</span> إِلَخ. وَانْظُر مَنَاقِب الْفَخر <span class="c2">(ص ١٠٨)</span> .<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٢٤١ ٤ <span class="c2">(الطَّائِفَة ثَلَاثَة فَأكْثر)</span> رَاجع فى مَنَاقِب الْفَخر <span class="c2">(ص ٩٨- ٩٩)</span> : اعْتِرَاض أَبى بكر بن دَاوُد، على هَذَا ورد الْفَخر عَلَيْهِ. لجودته وَفَائِدَته.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٢٤٢ ٣ <span class="c2">(والمطلقات)</span> : بِفَتْح اللَّام<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>